tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE patient_demographics (
    patient_id INT,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(50),
    address TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE doctor_notes (
    note_id INT,
    patient_id INT,
    date DATE,
    diagnosis TEXT,
    medication TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE appointments (
    appointment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    doctor_id INT,
    appointment_date DATE,
    reason TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE appointments (
  appointment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  doctor_id INT,
  appointment_date DATE,
  appointment_time TIME
);
